    controller participant can 
       AddTeammate: ContractId ParticipantSubmission 
        with 
          newChallengeId: Text 
          participantCurrent: Party 
          participantToAdd: Party
        do create this with challengeId=newChallengeId, participant=participantCurrent, participants=participantToAdd::participants
        

